      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DIVORCE PAPERS (2) finds it hard to break through. Finished second (19.90) at this track latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from five attempts. Winning claims. SHE'S ATHLETIC (7) flew the lids from out wide with a slick early split but ran over at the finish when a narrow fifth (20.09) over 352m at this track. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Better than last start and can bounce back. LONE PILOT (8) should be thereabouts after filling a top-three at this track and distance most recently.",
